## Stream Modes (OBS Scenes)

| Mode | What's Happening | Music |
|------|-----------------|-------|
| **Outside Inn Warmup** | Marwan's lo-fi animation, member names scrolling | Carson's music, 100% |
| **Writing Stream** | Facecam + Notion/AI screen share, the actual work | Carson's music, 20–30% background |
| **Gaming Stream** | Facecam + game capture | Carson's music, 20–30% background or off |
| **Outside Inn Cooldown** | Same as warmup — wind-down, outro | Carson's music, 100% |
| **Ambient Loop (offline)** | Outside Inn animation runs on YouTube when not live | Carson's music, 100% |

> **Scene switching:** Warmup → Live → Cooldown → Ambient Loop. Managed via Stream Deck. Target: one-button transitions between all modes.

